<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="satisfaction-n">satisfaction <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌsætɪs'fækʃn/    美 /ˌsætɪs'fækʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>满意；满足；乐事</strong></h4>
<p>反 dissatisfaction ： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>feeling / sense of satisfaction</strong> 
满足感</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>expressed</strong> her <strong>satisfaction with / at</strong> the result.
她对结果表示满意。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="to-sbs-satisfaction">to sb’s satisfaction</h3>
<p>1.<strong>令某人满意的是：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To my satisfaction, I have passed the examination.
我通过了考试，心满意足。</p></div>

<h3 id="with-satisfaction">with satisfaction</h3>
<p>1.<strong>满意地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He looked at his students with great satisfaction. 
他十分满意地看着学生们。</p></div></div>